snippet.title: Refind Self: The Personality Test Game - PGS Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Refind Self: The Personality Test Game is an adventure game and personality test rolled into one, coming to Steam, Google Play, and the App Store in November 2023!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2514960

■ Release Date: November 14, 2023
■ MSRP: Steam $7.99 | Google Play / App Store $3.99
■ Developer: Lizardry
■ Publisher: PLAYISM
■ Official Website: https://playism.com/game/refindself/
